<p>Losing a mother is an unbearable pain. These messages aim to offer the family heartfelt condolences and strength during this difficult time.</p>
<li>Thinking of you all and sending strength during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Your mother was a wonderful woman, and she will be deeply missed.</li>
<li>My heart aches for your loss. May precious memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy on the passing of your beloved mother.</li>
<li>Sending you love and prayers during this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>May your mother's memory be a blessing to you all.</li>
<li>So sorry for your loss.  Holding you all in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>Words can't express the sadness I feel. Thinking of you.</li>
<li>I'm heartbroken for your loss. May her memory be eternal.</li>
<li>Cherishing the memories of your wonderful mother.  My deepest condolences.</li>
<li>Sending love and support to you and your family.</li>
<li>Your mother's kindness and spirit will be remembered forever.</li>
